Band History

On July 27, 2012, the band released a new EP entitled Home At Last with their new album Clash of the Gods following on August 31 under Napalm Records. They went on to play a handful of shows in the UK and Europe from early to late 2012 before and after the album's release and then went all out the year of 2013 in Europe and played a few shows in Brazil in support of the album.

On 20 March 2014, the band revealed the artwork for their new studio album titled Return of the Reaper which is scheduled to be released on 11 July via their current label Napalm Records.
